ing: 1 (6 ounce) can frozen pineapple juice concentrate
des: "A summery drink that can be made year-round to brighten the mood! Vanilla, honey, bananas, pineapple, and cinnamon on top!"
ins: In a blender, blend the milk, water, pineapple juice concentrate, sugar, vanilla extract, banana, and ice cubes until smooth. Sprinkle with cinnamon, and serve immediately.
